  "StockRole": "Gladiator",
  "YangsThoughts": "The Yun Qi came out of Firefly Foundry's Sea Fox partnership and was built specifically to give Firefly Stables a competitive medium-class entry in the Solaris VII games, which had been a gap in the stable's lineup. Arena design requires a different kind of thinking than field hardware, and whoever drew this one up understood that a medium mech needs to be dangerous at every range to survive against opponents who will probe for weaknesses before committing. Fitting a Clan Gauss Rifle into a 50-ton frame without sacrificing close-range options is not a trivial engineering problem, and they solved it well.",
